能用最新的技术还原赫本年轻时的样子，甚至是彩色的图片，科技的进步还是令我挺有感触的。

使用chilloutmix-NI制作，lora尺寸为512*768，请不要使用超过此尺寸过多的初始大小。请不要使用过多的prompt tags。

I made a lora of Audrey Hepburn. Hepburn is a star I have admired since my childhood. She not only has a beautiful appearance, but also has an angelic heart.

I can use the latest technology to restore Hepburn's youthful appearance, even colorful pictures. I am very touched by the advancement of technology.

Made with chilloutmix-NI.The size of lora is 512*768, please do not use an initial size that exceeds this size too much.please do not use too many tags.
